.TH HEIRLOOM-PORT-WORLD 7 "2026-07-02" "Heirloom Darwin port" "Workspace"
.SH NAME
heirloom-port-world \- build + install all 5 companion packages
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B make world
.SH DESCRIPTION
Runs
.B make phase1 phase2 phase3 phase4 phase5
in order, each of which invokes
.BR "build install"
in the corresponding companion repo under
.IR \$(SIBLINGS)/heirloom-<pkg>-darwin .
Requires that every companion repo already be cloned; use
.B make clone-companions
to fetch missing ones.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR heirloom-port-clone-companions (7),
.BR heirloom-port-lifecycle (7)
